'''Alice''' is the girlfriend of [[Charlotte]].

==History==
Alice came to the hospital when she learned that her girlfriend, Charlotte, had been burned in a wildfire, despite Charlotte having told her she was okay.

==Relationships==
===Romantic===
She is dating [[Charlotte]].
